704436f-b.title: Brooklyn: Franklin Avenue - Kent Avenue
704436f-b.text:
Franklin Avenue, east from near Sent Avenue. The curve in the
trolley tracks is at Franklin Avenue.
View 3 shows an ornsmental building, adjoining the northeast
corner 8f Nent Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  Au~ust 24, 1941
NO RIPPODUCTIONS  Views 1-3
